{"tid":1176624,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先係旺角撞到個死金毛mk爭啲要同佢開片","createTime":"2019-05-29T10:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T14:32:25.000Z","uid":218575,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d425f3a56ac35afb9c4a7f58eaecfc20711ae350","tid":1176624,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"話說我頭先係旺角銀行中心個到一路行<br />\n一路掛住撳電話 唔小心撞到個金毛mk <br />\n佢眼超超咁望住我行走咗 <br />\n呢個時候我又唔想失威 係佢轉身走咗之後<br />\n 我講咗句：啤乜撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後個mk竟然沖埋黎想打我<br />\n<br />\n呀屌佢老母 咁遠都聽到 又幾好耳力<br />\n好彩我跑得快 如果唔係見佢一鑊打佢一鑊<br />\n<br />\n大家留意 我跑唔係因為我驚<br />\n我係怕我錯手打死佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5c931712a9b24bdfd31a130b5193c3aea910a5","tid":1176624,"uid":84551,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:44:04.000Z","msg":"好威威啊ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9224e480adcc286e0c6e36a0b11b0943986c8269","tid":1176624,"uid":72867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:44:28.000Z","msg":"你有冇腹肌先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c00fe6f130e00a8d5ace7c1e40326fe4a27c31","tid":1176624,"uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"冇撞！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小次郎！！！"},{"pid":"058f06b1436d97fe675a6e911b5814f0eacce62f","tid":1176624,"uid":186844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5c00fe6f130e00a8d5ace7c1e40326fe4a27c31","tid":1176624,"uid":71508,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"冇撞！！！<br /